sequenceDiagram
    participant User as External Client
    participant GW as Gateway (maas-default-gateway)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS Terminate
    participant BBR as payload-processing (BBR)<br/>9004/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant Auth as Authorino<br/>(Kuadrant AuthPolicy)
    participant MaaSAPI as maas-api<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Limit as Limitador<br/>(TokenRateLimitPolicy)
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant KServe as KServe InferenceService<br/>HTTPS
    participant ExtLLM as External LLM Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,ExtLLM: Flow 1: User Inference Request (API Key)
    User->>GW: POST /{ns}/{model}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer sk-oai-*
    GW->>BBR: gRPC ext-proc (9004/TCP TLS SIMPLE)<br/>Extract model, resolve provider
    BBR-->>GW: X-Gateway-Model-Name header + upstream routing
    GW->>Auth: AuthPolicy evaluation
    Auth->>MaaSAPI: POST /internal/v1/api-keys/validate<br/>(NetworkPolicy, no auth)
    MaaSAPI->>PG: SELECT api_key (SHA-256 lookup)
    PG-->>MaaSAPI: Key metadata + groups
    MaaSAPI-->>Auth: Validation result (user, groups, subscription)
    Auth->>MaaSAPI: POST /internal/v1/subscriptions/select<br/>(NetworkPolicy, no auth)
    MaaSAPI-->>Auth: Selected subscription + rate limits
    Auth-->>GW: Auth decision (allow/deny)
    GW->>Limit: TokenRateLimitPolicy check
    Limit-->>GW: Rate limit decision
    alt Internal Model (KServe)
        GW->>KServe: Forward request (mTLS)
        KServe-->>GW: Inference response
    else External Model
        Note over BBR: BBR injects provider API key,<br/>strips original auth header
        GW->>ExtLLM: Forward request (TLS SIMPLE)<br/>Auth: Provider API key (injected)
        ExtLLM-->>GW: Inference response
    end
    GW-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User,ExtLLM: Flow 2: User API Key Management
    User->>GW: POST /v1/api-keys<br/>Auth: OpenShift Bearer token
    GW->>Auth: AuthPolicy evaluation
    Auth->>Auth: kubernetesTokenReview (K8s API 443/TCP)
    Auth-->>GW: Auth decision + X-MaaS-Username/Group headers
    GW->>MaaSAPI: POST /v1/api-keys (8443/TCP HTTPS)
    MaaSAPI->>MaaSAPI: SubjectAccessReview (K8s API 443/TCP)
    MaaSAPI->>PG: INSERT api_key (hashed)
    PG-->>MaaSAPI: Stored
    MaaSAPI-->>GW: API key (plaintext, shown once)
    GW-->>User: {"api_key": "sk-oai-..."}

    Note over User,ExtLLM: Flow 3: ExternalModel Routing
    User->>GW: POST /{ns}/{extmodel}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer token
    GW->>BBR: gRPC ext-proc (9004/TCP TLS)
    BBR->>BBR: Read ExternalModel CR + credentialRef Secret<br/>(K8s API 443/TCP)
    BBR-->>GW: Provider endpoint + injected API key
    GW->>Auth: AuthPolicy evaluation
    Auth-->>GW: Auth decision
    GW->>Limit: Rate limit check
    Limit-->>GW: Rate decision
    GW->>ExtLLM: Forward via Istio ServiceEntry<br/>TLS SIMPLE (DestinationRule)<br/>Auth: Provider API key
    ExtLLM-->>GW: Response
    GW-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User,ExtLLM: Flow 4: Tenant Platform Reconciliation
    Note over MaaSAPI: maas-controller watches Tenant CR
    MaaSAPI->>MaaSAPI: Kustomize build (in-process)
    MaaSAPI->>MaaSAPI: Post-render transforms<br/>(gateway config, OIDC, telemetry)
    MaaSAPI->>MaaSAPI: Server-side apply to K8s API<br/>(field manager: maas-controller)
    MaaSAPI->>MaaSAPI: Check deployment readiness
